                     <br/>MEDICAL GASES<br/>LIQUID OXYGEN, U.S.P. DELIVERY TAG<br/>FILLED BY<br/>WELDERS SUPPLY A RAIMY CORPORATION<br/>1628 CASCADE STREET – ERIE, PA 16502<br/>(814) 454-1563 – FAX (814) 455-1059<br/>(800) 352-0945<br/>THIS VESSEL CONTAINS OXYGEN USP (see reverse side for test results)<br/>OXYGEN PRODUCED BY THE AIR LIQUEFACTION PROCESS<br/>O.D.T.</paragraph>
